data.title: Who is from your town?
data.text:
Always happy to harvest information from the Cockeyed.com readership, I asked a question about Cockeyed.com readers' local knowledge.

The question was, "Who is from your town?"

Sacramento is the ancestral home to a few celebrities, chief among them Ms. Molly Ringwald and Mr. Tom Hanks. Here are the answers, in alphabetical order, by city. Many cities had more than one answer submitted. Some answers were edited.
